{
  "video_id": "7_RGn75JcZ8",
  "title": "Addiction is a disease. We should treat it like one | Michael Botticelli",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12820.0,
      "end_time": 15660.0,
      "text": "Twenty-eight years ago, I was a broken man."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16580.0,
      "end_time": 19459.0,
      "text": "And you probably wouldn&#39;t be able to tell that if you met me."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20600.0,
      "end_time": 23939.0,
      "text": "I had a good job at a well-respected academic institution."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24660.0,
      "end_time": 25940.0,
      "text": "I dressed well, of course."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27580.0,
      "end_time": 29299.0,
      "text": "But my insides were rotting away."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 30460.0,
      "end_time": 33420.0,
      "text": "You see, I grew up in a family riddled with addiction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 34460.0,
      "end_time": 35920.0,
      "text": "and as a kid, I also struggled"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 35944.0,
      "end_time": 38716.0,
      "text": "with coming to terms with my own sexuality."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38740.0,
      "end_time": 41760.0,
      "text": "And even though I couldn&#39;t name it then,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 41100.0,
      "end_time": 43116.0,
      "text": "growing up as a gay kid"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43140.0,
      "end_time": 46900.0,
      "text": "just compounded my issues of isolation and insecurities."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 48340.0,
      "end_time": 50300.0,
      "text": "But drinking took all of that away."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 52660.0,
      "end_time": 55779.0,
      "text": "Like many, I drank at an early age."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 56660.0,
      "end_time": 58860.0,
      "text": "I continued to drink my way through college."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 59660.0,
      "end_time": 62476.0,
      "text": "And when I finally did come out in the early 1980s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 62500.0,
      "end_time": 65316.0,
      "text": "about the only places to meet other gay people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 65340.0,
      "end_time": 66540.0,
      "text": "to socialize,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 67340.0,
      "end_time": 69200.0,
      "text": "to be yourself, were gay bars."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 70180.0,
      "end_time": 71660.0,
      "text": "And what do you do in gay bars?"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 72300.0,
      "end_time": 73875.0,
      "text": "You drink."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 73900.0,
      "end_time": 75516.0,
      "text": "And I did --"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 75540.0,
      "end_time": 76740.0,
      "text": "a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 77580.0,
      "end_time": 78940.0,
      "text": "My story is not unique."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 79780.0,
      "end_time": 83460.0,
      "text": "Like millions of Americans, my disease progressed undiagnosed."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 84220.0,
      "end_time": 86196.0,
      "text": "It took me to people and places and things"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 86220.0,
      "end_time": 87700.0,
      "text": "that I never would have chosen."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 89200.0,
      "end_time": 91836.0,
      "text": "It wasn&#39;t until an intersection with the law"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 91860.0,
      "end_time": 95600.0,
      "text": "gave me an \"opportunity\" to get care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 95700.0,
      "end_time": 97620.0,
      "text": "that I began my journey of recovery."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 98820.0,
      "end_time": 102820.0,
      "text": "My journey of recovery has been filled with love and with joy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 103780.0,
      "end_time": 105756.0,
      "text": "but it hasn&#39;t been without pain."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 105780.0,
      "end_time": 109756.0,
      "text": "Like many of you, I&#39;ve lost too many friends and family to this disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 109780.0,
      "end_time": 111716.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve heard too many heartbreaking stories"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 111740.0,
      "end_time": 113899.0,
      "text": "of people who&#39;ve lost loved ones to addiction."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 114580.0,
      "end_time": 117940.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;ve also lost countless friends to HIV and AIDS."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 118980.0,
      "end_time": 122516.0,
      "text": "Our current opioid epidemic and the AIDS epidemic"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 122540.0,
      "end_time": 124300.0,
      "text": "tragically have much in common."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 125860.0,
      "end_time": 129699.0,
      "text": "Right now, we are in the midst of one of the greatest health crises of our time."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 131100.0,
      "end_time": 135436.0,
      "text": "During 2014 alone, 28,000 people"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 135460.0,
      "end_time": 139900.0,
      "text": "died of drug overdoses associated with prescription drugs and heroin."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 141980.0,
      "end_time": 146579.0,
      "text": "During the 1980s, scores of people were dying from HIV and AIDS."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 147620.0,
      "end_time": 149260.0,
      "text": "Public officials ignored it."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 150340.0,
      "end_time": 152260.0,
      "text": "Some wouldn&#39;t even utter the words."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 153620.0,
      "end_time": 155260.0,
      "text": "They didn&#39;t want treatment."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 156100.0,
      "end_time": 159380.0,
      "text": "And tragically, there are many parallels with our current epidemic."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 160540.0,
      "end_time": 162179.0,
      "text": "Some called it the gay plague."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 163340.0,
      "end_time": 164900.0,
      "text": "They called for quarantines."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 166260.0,
      "end_time": 169380.0,
      "text": "They wanted to separate the innocent victims from the rest of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 171940.0,
      "end_time": 174276.0,
      "text": "I was afraid we were losing this battle"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 174300.0,
      "end_time": 177260.0,
      "text": "because people were blaming us for being sick."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 178620.0,
      "end_time": 181940.0,
      "text": "Public policy was being held hostage by stigma and fear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 183700.0,
      "end_time": 184956.0,
      "text": "and also held hostage"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 184980.0,
      "end_time": 190579.0,
      "text": "were compassion, care, research, recovery and treatment."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 191460.0,
      "end_time": 192660.0,
      "text": "But we changed all that."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 194300.0,
      "end_time": 196876.0,
      "text": "Because out of the pain of those deaths,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 196900.0,
      "end_time": 199620.0,
      "text": "we saw a social and political movement."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 200620.0,
      "end_time": 203980.0,
      "text": "AIDS galvanized us into action;"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 204740.0,
      "end_time": 208980.0,
      "text": "to stand up, to speak up and to act out."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 210200.0,
      "end_time": 212580.0,
      "text": "And it also galvanized the LGBT movement."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 214340.0,
      "end_time": 216276.0,
      "text": "We knew we were in a battle for our lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 216300.0,
      "end_time": 217860.0,
      "text": "because silence equaled death,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 218780.0,
      "end_time": 221780.0,
      "text": "but we changed, and we made things happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 222580.0,
      "end_time": 224876.0,
      "text": "And right now, we have the potential"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 224900.0,
      "end_time": 227900.0,
      "text": "to see the end of HIV/AIDS in our lifetime."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 230300.0,
      "end_time": 233116.0,
      "text": "These changes came in no small part"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 233140.0,
      "end_time": 236260.0,
      "text": "by the courageous, yet simple decision"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 236980.0,
      "end_time": 238420.0,
      "text": "for people to come out"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 239260.0,
      "end_time": 244179.0,
      "text": "to their neighbors, to their friends, to their families"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 245300.0,
      "end_time": 246500.0,
      "text": "and to their coworkers."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 248380.0,
      "end_time": 251220.0,
      "text": "Years ago, I was a volunteer for the Names Project."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 252200.0,
      "end_time": 255396.0,
      "text": "This was an effort started by Cleve Jones in San Francisco"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 255420.0,
      "end_time": 257396.0,
      "text": "to show that people who died of AIDS"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 257420.00000000003,
      "end_time": 258620.00000000003,
      "text": "had names"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 259380.0,
      "end_time": 262180.0,
      "text": "and faces and families"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 263140.0,
      "end_time": 264620.0,
      "text": "and people who loved them."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 266940.0,
      "end_time": 271779.0,
      "text": "I still recall unfolding the AIDS memorial quilt"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 272740.0,
      "end_time": 278300.0,
      "text": "on the National Mall on a brilliant day in October, 1988."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 283260.0,
      "end_time": 284940.0,
      "text": "So fast forward to 2015."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 286300.0,
      "end_time": 290580.0,
      "text": "The Supreme Court&#39;s decision to strike down the ban on same-sex marriage."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 291580.0,
      "end_time": 294756.0,
      "text": "My husband, Dave, and I walk over to the steps of the Supreme Court"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 294780.0,
      "end_time": 297715.0,
      "text": "to celebrate that decision with so many other people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 297740.0,
      "end_time": 303116.0,
      "text": "and I couldn&#39;t help but think how far we came around LGBT rights"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 303140.0,
      "end_time": 307940.0,
      "text": "and yet how far we needed to go around issues of addiction."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 309940.0,
      "end_time": 311796.0,
      "text": "When I was nominated by President Obama"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 311820.0,
      "end_time": 313996.0,
      "text": "to be his Director of Drug Policy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 314200.0,
      "end_time": 317659.0,
      "text": "I was very open about my recovery and about the fact that I was a gay man."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 318540.0,
      "end_time": 320876.0,
      "text": "And at no point during my confirmation process --"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 320900.0,
      "end_time": 322436.0,
      "text": "at least that I know of --"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 322460.0,
      "end_time": 326436.0,
      "text": "did the fact that I was a gay man come to bear on my candidacy"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 326460.0,
      "end_time": 328260.0,
      "text": "or my fitness to do this job."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 329580.0,
      "end_time": 330780.0,
      "text": "But my addiction did."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 332500.0,
      "end_time": 335956.0,
      "text": "At one point, a congressional staffer said that there was no way"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 335980.0,
      "end_time": 338836.0,
      "text": "that I was going to be confirmed by the United States Senate"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 338860.0,
      "end_time": 340436.0,
      "text": "because of my past,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 340460.0,
      "end_time": 343876.0,
      "text": "despite the fact that I had been in recovery for over 20 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 343900.0,
      "end_time": 345116.0,
      "text": "and despite the fact"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 345140.0,
      "end_time": 348116.0,
      "text": "that this job takes a little bit of knowledge around addiction."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 348140.0,
      "end_time": 349620.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 351460.0,
      "end_time": 354395.0,
      "text": "So, you know, this is the stigma"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 354420.0,
      "end_time": 356476.0,
      "text": "that people with substance use disorders"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 356500.0,
      "end_time": 357900.0,
      "text": "face every single day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 358700.0,
      "end_time": 360276.0,
      "text": "and you know, I have to tell you"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 360300.0,
      "end_time": 363756.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s still why I&#39;m more comfortable coming out as a gay man"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 363780.0,
      "end_time": 366299.0,
      "text": "than I am as a person with a history of addiction."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 367460.0,
      "end_time": 370859.0,
      "text": "Nearly every family in America is affected by addiction."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 371580.0,
      "end_time": 377990.0,
      "text": "Yet, unfortunately, too often, it&#39;s not talked about openly and honestly."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 377980.0,
      "end_time": 379636.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s whispered about."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 379660.0,
      "end_time": 382200.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s met with derision and scorn."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 383140.0,
      "end_time": 387780.0,
      "text": "We hear these stories, time and time again, on TV, online,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 388580.0,
      "end_time": 392200.0,
      "text": "we hear it from public officials, and we hear it from family and friends."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 393540.0,
      "end_time": 396340.0,
      "text": "And those of us with an addiction, we hear those voices,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 397380.0,
      "end_time": 401500.0,
      "text": "and somehow we believe that we are less deserving of care and treatment."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 402860.0,
      "end_time": 406236.0,
      "text": "Today in the United States, only one in nine people"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 406260.0,
      "end_time": 408796.0,
      "text": "get care and treatment for their disorder."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 408820.0,
      "end_time": 410396.0,
      "text": "One in nine."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 410420.0,
      "end_time": 411620.0,
      "text": "Think about that."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 412420.0,
      "end_time": 415476.0,
      "text": "Generally, people with other diseases get care and treatment."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 415500.0,
      "end_time": 417476.0,
      "text": "If you have cancer, you get treatment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 417500.0,
      "end_time": 419516.0,
      "text": "if you have diabetes, you get treatment."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 419540.0,
      "end_time": 420876.0,
      "text": "If you have a heart attack,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 420900.0,
      "end_time": 423599.0,
      "text": "you get emergency services, and you get referred to care."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 425200.0,
      "end_time": 428236.0,
      "text": "But somehow people with addiction have to wait for treatment"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 428260.0,
      "end_time": 430380.0,
      "text": "or often can&#39;t get when they need it."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 431620.0,
      "end_time": 435580.0,
      "text": "And left untreated, addiction has significant, dire consequences."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 436180.0,
      "end_time": 439500.0,
      "text": "And for many people that means death or incarceration."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 440820.0,
      "end_time": 442407.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve been down that road before."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 443220.0,
      "end_time": 444636.0,
      "text": "For too long our country felt"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 444660.0,
      "end_time": 446980.0,
      "text": "like we could arrest our way out of this problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 447700.0,
      "end_time": 448979.0,
      "text": "But we know that we can&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 450500.0,
      "end_time": 452876.0,
      "text": "Decades of scientific research has shown"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 452900.0,
      "end_time": 455360.0,
      "text": "that this is a medical issue --"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 455600.0,
      "end_time": 457636.0,
      "text": "that this is a chronic medical condition"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 457660.0,
      "end_time": 460540.0,
      "text": "that people inherit and that people develop."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 461820.0,
      "end_time": 465219.0,
      "text": "So the Obama administration has taken a different tack on drug policy."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 466380.0,
      "end_time": 469316.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve developed and implemented a comprehensive plan"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 469340.0,
      "end_time": 472715.0,
      "text": "to expand prevention services, treatment services,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 472740.0,
      "end_time": 475380.0,
      "text": "early intervention and recovery support."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 476620.0,
      "end_time": 478405.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve pushed criminal justice reform."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 479460.0,
      "end_time": 482180.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve knocked down barriers to give people second chances."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 482700.0,
      "end_time": 486116.0,
      "text": "We see public health and public safety officials working hand in hand"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 486140.0,
      "end_time": 487340.0,
      "text": "at the community level."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 488300.0,
      "end_time": 491476.0,
      "text": "We see police chiefs across the country guiding people to treatment"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 491500.0,
      "end_time": 493140.0,
      "text": "instead of jail and incarceration."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 494220.0,
      "end_time": 497116.0,
      "text": "We see law enforcement and other first responders"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 497140.0,
      "end_time": 501979.0,
      "text": "reversing overdoses with naloxone to give people a second chance for care."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 503460.0,
      "end_time": 506116.0,
      "text": "The Affordable Care Act is the biggest expansion"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 506140.0,
      "end_time": 509395.0,
      "text": "of substance use disorder treatment in a generation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 509420.0,
      "end_time": 513460.0,
      "text": "and it also calls for the integration of treatment services within primary care."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 516100.0,
      "end_time": 520140.0,
      "text": "But fundamentally, all of this work is not enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 520659.0,
      "end_time": 524675.0,
      "text": "Unless we change the way that we view people with addiction"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 524700.0,
      "end_time": 525900.0,
      "text": "in the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 527220.0,
      "end_time": 530796.0,
      "text": "Years ago when I finally understood that I had a problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 530820.0,
      "end_time": 532955.0,
      "text": "and I knew that I needed help,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 532979.0,
      "end_time": 534619.0,
      "text": "I was too afraid to ask for it."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 536140.0,
      "end_time": 540340.0,
      "text": "I felt that people would think I was stupid, that I was weak-willed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 541340.0,
      "end_time": 543700.0,
      "text": "that I was morally flawed."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 545700.0,
      "end_time": 549220.0,
      "text": "But I talk about my recovery because I want to make change."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 550600.0,
      "end_time": 555996.0,
      "text": "I want us to see that we need to be open and candid about who we are"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 556200.0,
      "end_time": 557220.0,
      "text": "and what we can do."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 558140.0,
      "end_time": 560516.0,
      "text": "I am public about my own recovery"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 560540.0,
      "end_time": 562459.0,
      "text": "not to be self-congratulatory."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 563260.0,
      "end_time": 567116.0,
      "text": "I am open about my own recovery to change public opinion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 567140.0,
      "end_time": 569360.0,
      "text": "to change public policy"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 569600.0,
      "end_time": 572955.0,
      "text": "and to change the course of this epidemic and empower the millions of Americans"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 572980.0,
      "end_time": 574836.0,
      "text": "who struggle with this journey"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 574860.0,
      "end_time": 576820.0,
      "text": "to be open and candid about who they are."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 578460.0,
      "end_time": 580780.0,
      "text": "People are more than their disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 581700.0,
      "end_time": 584996.0,
      "text": "And all of us have the opportunity to change public opinion"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 585200.0,
      "end_time": 586660.0,
      "text": "and to change public policy."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 587820.0,
      "end_time": 590100.0,
      "text": "All of us know someone who has an addiction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 591100.0,
      "end_time": 593360.0,
      "text": "and all of us can do our part"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 593600.0,
      "end_time": 597219.0,
      "text": "to change how we view people with addiction in the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 598220.0,
      "end_time": 600636.0,
      "text": "So when you see someone with an addiction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 600660.0,
      "end_time": 606339.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t think of a drunk or a junkie or an addict or an abuser --"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 607500.0,
      "end_time": 608700.0,
      "text": "see a person;"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 609860.0,
      "end_time": 611356.0,
      "text": "offer them help;"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 611380.0,
      "end_time": 613100.0,
      "text": "give them kindness and compassion."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 614180.0,
      "end_time": 616396.0,
      "text": "And together, we can be part"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 616420.0,
      "end_time": 618476.0,
      "text": "of a growing movement in the United States"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 618500.0,
      "end_time": 620580.0,
      "text": "to change how we view people with addiction."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 621300.0,
      "end_time": 623420.0,
      "text": "Together we can change public policy."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 624260.0,
      "end_time": 628156.0,
      "text": "We can ensure that people get care when they need it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 628180.0,
      "end_time": 629859.0,
      "text": "just like any other disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 630860.0,
      "end_time": 634556.0,
      "text": "We can be part of a growing, unstoppable movement"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 634580.0,
      "end_time": 637596.0,
      "text": "to have millions of Americans enter recovery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 637620.0,
      "end_time": 639716.0,
      "text": "and put an end to this epidemic."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 639740.0,
      "end_time": 640956.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 640980.0,
      "end_time": 643356.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}